divs: Sighting DetailsI woke to take a pee opened my door and saw two orbs in the sky.at first i thought they may be airplanes on aproach to land but then realized that the balls of light were not planes but in fact some strange type of craft...these two craft moved silently and seemed to be attached to each other in some way at times and at other times they wete seperate from each other.i ran to grab my phone when the objects were about to pass me overhead... I snapped 7photos that originaly i thought the camera was unable to capture the ufos. Only later that day did i realize that there wete images to look at.. when these objects left they did not fly away but simply vanished from the air...like a lightswitch had turned them off...it should be noted that one of the two craft headed off in the north east direction towards thurston it was this craft that dematerialized first then the one going north dematerialized about four minutes after tje first one... of course i was stunned and could hardly believe what had just happened.. Also there have been multiple sightings of strange craft in the sky in eugene this month...
